.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: purple, turquise, pink, amber, apricot
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, french, american, german, chinese
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, davidoff, bolivar, vegafina, montecristo
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-lemonade, cola, lemonade, mirinda, fanta
5 different pets are kept: pony, ferret, mouse, guinea-pig, rabbit

1. the russian is the person who likes purple
2. the french is the owner of the pony
3. the person drinking soy-lemonade is the person who likes turquise
4. the american is the person drinking cola
5. the person who likes turquise is to the right of the person who likes pink
6. the dunhill-smoker is the owner of the rabbit
7. the davidoff-smoker is the person who likes amber
8. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle
9. the german is on the far left
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret
11. the davidoff-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig
12. the vegafina-smoker is the person drinking mirinda
13. the chinese is the montecristo-smoker
14. the german is to the left or right of the person who likes apricot

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   german	|    american	|     russian	|    french	|    chinese	|
| Color		|    amber	|      apricot	|      purple	|     pink	|     turquise	|
| Beverage	|     fanta	|      cola	|      lemonade	| mirinda	|     soy-lemonade	|
| Cigar		|     davidoff	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| vegafina	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     ferret	|     guinea-pig	|     rabbit	|     pony	|     mouse	|
